<h2 class="bold font-l">Bob Saving the Betas</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In order to stop the Betas from going through with the prank, Bob interrupts the ceremony and gives a speech to the audience while telling the Betas the truth. </p>
